latestPosts.caption:
Dinner, but make it 36floors high✨🍷
An evening above the city, where every detail whispers luxury.✨
Perched on the 36th floor, @noxbombay @westinmumbaipowai redefines fine dining with its artfully curated cocktails, globally inspired cuisine, and the most breathtaking view of Powai Lake shimmering under city lights.
From the perfectly charred prawns and rich saffron-infused chicken to the delicate balance of umami on our truffle mushroom pizza, every bite was an experience in itself.
Add to that a cocktail menu that rivals the skyline? Simply unforgettable.
@noxbombay isn’t just a restaurant. It’s a celebration of elevated taste, timeless elegance, and that rare kind of luxury you don’t just see-you feel.”

#NOXatWestin #FineDiningMumbai #PowaiLakeViews #LuxuryEvenings #CocktailCulture #GastronomyWithAView #ElevatedExperiences #WestinDiaries #36FloorsAboveOrdinary
